# =============================================================
# .gitignore — Digital Omamori
# Usage: run `git init` directly in this folder (plainsafe/). This file keeps
#        internal / sensitive / oversized files out of the public repo, so no
#        separate "clean copy" is needed (nothing to keep in sync, no drift).
# =============================================================

# --- 1. Keys / credentials (hard rule: never in the repo) ---
.config.json
.cert/
*.pem
*.key
GEMINI_KEY.txt
gcp-key.json

# --- 2. Dependencies / runtime artifacts (regenerable) ---
node_modules/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
backup/
data/*.tmp
.DS_Store

# --- 3. Internal history / old versions (not product, oversized) ---
snapshots/          # internal milestone snapshots (kept locally)
legacy/             # old phone-frame version

# --- 4. Internal working files (contain local paths or working notes) ---
*.command           # launcher scripts (contain local absolute paths)
STANDARDS.md        # internal working standards, not a product doc
data/kuji_content_draft.md   # internal omikuji authoring draft (kuji.json is the shipped data)

# --- 5. QA / test-only assets (not app data) ---
# Note: photos/ is a seed demo asset and IS shipped (card thumbnails on deploy/clone);
#       only QA test images + an AI-generated test image are excluded:
photos/heic-test-front.heic
photos/muji-test-front.png
photos/muji-test2-front.png
photos/pn-front.png
data/imagefable.png  # 2.5MB AI-generated Lens QA test image, not app data

# =============================================================
# Shipped to the public repo (for reference):
#   index.html server.py storage.py sw.js manifest.json
#   Dockerfile requirements.txt package.json
#   README.md CHANGELOG.md RUN.md DEPLOY_GUIDE.md .gcloudignore .dockerignore
#   app/  data/(JSON packs)  photos/(1 seed)  tests/(suites + fixtures)
# =============================================================

# repo hygiene 2026-07-06: internal boxes, never ship
_dev_only/
_archive/
_to_be_deleted/
